{
  "texts": [
    "Try to answer these questions to get a better understanding of Newton's cradle",
    "Cognitive Elaboration (Berthold & M. Nückles et al., 2007) If the student's answer is incomplete, encourage the student to elaborate on aspects that were missing without giving the correct answer You're right, the metal balls hit each other.",
    "But that's only part of the story.",
    "Can you perhaps say a little more about this?",
    "For example, what happens when one ball hits the others?"
  ]
}